# Checkbox — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/checkbox.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
- `.acko-checkbox` — inline-flex, items-start, gap-3, cursor-pointer, select-none
- `.acko-checkbox-native` — visually hidden native input
- `.acko-checkbox-box` — custom box with border `--color-control-border-selector`

### Sizes (via `.acko-checkbox-{size}`)
| Size | Box | Icon SVG | Label font |
|------|-----|----------|------------|
| sm | `--scale-16`, radius-sm | `--scale-10` | `--font-body-sm-size` |
| md | `--scale-20`, radius-md | `--scale-12` | `--font-body-md-size` |
| lg | `--scale-24`, radius-md | `--font-body-sm-size` | `--font-body-lg-size` |

### States
- `.acko-checkbox-checked` — box fills `--color-primary`
- `.acko-checkbox-indeterminate` — same fill, minus icon
- `.acko-checkbox-disabled` — subtle border, raised bg
- `.acko-checkbox-error` — error border

### Check Icon Animation
- `.acko-checkbox-icon` → `.acko-checkbox-icon-visible`: scale(0.3→1) with spring easing
